<h1>Education at Many Levels</h1>

<p>We will use bioluminescence as a model phenomenon to develop interdisciplinary curricula, resources, and education outreach events for all educational levels and backgrounds. Using bioluminescence, our hub will provide an example of how a unifying concept can be used to bridge disciplinary boundaries, while illustrating core ideas in STEM content and practice.
</p>
<br>

